    <entry>
      <title>react钩子函数（未完待续）</title>
      <link href="/2023/07/27/react-study/"/>
      <url>/2023/07/27/react-study/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="useStae"><a href="#useStae" class="headerlink" title="useStae"></a>useStae</h2><blockquote><p>state实际上是一个被React管理的变量<br>当我们通过setState()修改变量的值时，会触发组件的自动重新渲染<br>只有state值发生变化时，组件才会重新渲染<br>当state的值是一个对象时，修改时是使用新的对象去替换已有的对象<br>当通过setState去修改一个state时，并不表示修改当前的state，它修改的是下一次渲染的state值<br>setState()会触发组件的重新渲染，它是异步的</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight jsx"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> <span class="title class_">React</span> <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">&#x27;react&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123;useState&#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">&quot;react&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> <span class="string">&#x27;../index.css&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// useState</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="title function_">MyNum</span> = (<span class="params"></span>) =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">let</span> [num,setNum ] = <span class="title function_">useState</span>(<span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="title function_">addBtn</span> = (<span class="params"></span>) =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="title function_">setNum</span>(<span class="function"><span class="params">prevState</span>=&gt;</span>prevState+<span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="title function_">reduceBtn</span> = (<span class="params"></span>) =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="title function_">setNum</span>(<span class="function"><span class="params">prevState</span> =&gt;</span> prevState-<span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> (</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">className</span>=<span class="string">&quot;box&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml">            <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h2</span>&gt;</span>&#123;num&#125;<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h2</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml">            <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">button</span> <span class="attr">onClick</span>=<span class="string">&#123;reduceBtn&#125;</span>&gt;</span>-<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">button</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml">            <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">button</span> <span class="attr">onClick</span>=<span class="string">&#123;addBtn&#125;</span>&gt;</span>+<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">button</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml">        <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    );</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">export</span> <span class="keyword">default</span> <span class="title class_">MyNum</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em>num 代表原始值。<br>setNum用于修改值<br>useState(1)，1代表默认值<br>prevState : 修改一个state的值而需要依赖于前边的值进行计算时prevState 获取上一次state值，通过回调函数进行修改，保证每次拿到的是最新的值</em></p><h2 id="useRef"><a href="#useRef" class="headerlink" title="useRef"></a>useRef</h2><blockquote><p>钩子函数只能在函数组件或自定义钩子<br>钩子函数只能在函数组件中调用</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight jsx"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> <span class="title class_">React</span>, &#123;useRef&#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">&#x27;react&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> <span class="string">&#x27;../index.css&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 获取ref</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="title function_">GetRef</span> = (<span class="params"></span>) =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 创建一个容器</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">const</span> divRef = <span class="title function_">useRef</span>()</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// dom 属性在current容器中</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="title function_">alert</span>(divRef.<span class="property">current</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> (</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">className</span>=<span class="string">&quot;divClass&quot;</span> <span class="attr">ref</span>=<span class="string">&#123;divRef&#125;</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml">            </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml">        <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    );</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">export</span> <span class="keyword">default</span> <span class="title class_">GetRef</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em>当需要一个对象不会因为组件的渲染而改变的时候可以使用useRef</em></p><h2 id="useContext"><a href="#useContext" class="headerlink" title="useContext"></a>useContext</h2><blockquote><p>将Context对象设置到一个单独的模块中并设置为默认导出</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> <span class="title class_">React</span> <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">&quot;react&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="title class_">TestContext</span> = <span class="title class_">React</span>.<span class="title function_">createContext</span>(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">name</span>: <span class="string">&#x27;孙悟空&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">age</span>: <span class="number">18</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">gender</span>: <span class="string">&#x27;男&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">sayHello</span>: <span class="function">() =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="title function_">alert</span>(<span class="variable language_">this</span>.<span class="property">name</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">export</span> <span class="keyword">default</span> <span class="title class_">TestContext</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>如果想访问到Context中的数据，我们需要先将Context引入到当前组件中，然后通过Context对象访问其中的数据。</p></blockquote><p><strong>方式一</strong><br>通过Consumer标签来访问到Context中的数据</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> <span class="title class_">React</span> <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">&#x27;react&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> <span class="title class_">TestContext</span> <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">&quot;../../store/TestContext&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="title function_">A</span> = (<span class="params"></span>) =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> (</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">TestContext.Consumer</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml">            &#123;(ctx) =&gt; &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml">                return (</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml">                    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">ul</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml">                        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>&#123;ctx.name&#125;<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml">                        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>&#123;ctx.age&#125;<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml">                        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>&#123;ctx.gender&#125;<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml">                    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">ul</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml">                )</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml">            &#125;&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml">        <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">TestContext.Consumer</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    );</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">export</span> <span class="keyword">default</span> A;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>方式二</strong><br>通过useContext()，将Context对象作为参数传递给钩子函数</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> <span class="title class_">React</span>, &#123;useContext&#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">&#x27;react&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> <span class="title class_">TestContext</span> <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">&quot;../../store/TestContext&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="title function_">B</span> = (<span class="params"></span>) =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">const</span> ctx = <span class="title function_">useContext</span>(<span class="title class_">TestContext</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> (</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml">            <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">ul</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml">                <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>&#123;ctx.name&#125;<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml">                <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>&#123;ctx.age&#125;<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml">                <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>&#123;ctx.gender&#125;<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml">            <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">ul</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml">        <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    );</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">export</span> <span class="keyword">default</span> B;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>App中使用</p><blockquote><p>获取Context时，React会在它的外层查找最近的Provider，然后返回它的Context值。如果没有找到Provider，则会返回Context模块中设置的默认值。（<strong>就近原则</strong>）</p></blockquote><img src="/2023/07/27/react-study/react01.png" class="" title="在这里插入图片描述"><img src="/2023/07/27/react-study/react02.png" class="" title="在这里插入图片描述"><h2 id="useEffect"><a href="#useEffect" class="headerlink" title="useEffect"></a>useEffect</h2><blockquote><p>目前理解下来 作用类似于vue中的onMounted和onUpdated<br>又有点类似于vue中的watch<br>区别：<br>watch:<br>watch是依赖响应式对象，当依赖对象发生变化时候，，副作用函数会被触发执行<br>watch 第一个参数是依赖对象，第二个参数是副作用函数<br>useEffect:<br>第一个参数是副作用函数，第二个参数是一个依赖数组<br>当依赖数组中的变量发生变化时，副作用函数会重新执行（这一点我觉得类似于onUpdated）<br>如果不传依赖数组，默认副作用函数在每次组件渲染后都会执行（这一点我觉得类似于onMounted）</p></blockquote><p><em>使用案例</em></p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="title function_">useEffect</span>(<span class="function">() =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">       <span class="keyword">if</span> (ctx.<span class="property">totalAmount</span> === <span class="number">0</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">           <span class="title function_">setShowState</span>(<span class="literal">false</span>)</span><br><span class="line">           <span class="title function_">setShowCheckout</span>(<span class="literal">false</span>)</span><br><span class="line">       &#125;</span><br><span class="line">   &#125;,[ctx])</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="useReducer"><a href="#useReducer" class="headerlink" title="useReducer"></a>useReducer</h2><blockquote><p>Reducer主要是为了整合比较复杂的state</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> [state, dispatch] = <span class="title function_">useReducer</span>(reducer, initialArg, init);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote><p><strong>参数：</strong><br><em>reducer</em></p><blockquote><p>state所有操作都在reducer中进行，返回值是新的state值<br>reducer在执行的时候会收到两个参数<br>state  【当前最新的state】<br>action:【需要一个对象，对象中存储dispatch发送的指令】</p></blockquote><p><em>initialArg</em></p><blockquote><p>state的初始值</p></blockquote><p><strong>返回值</strong><br><em>state</em></p><blockquote><p>state的值</p></blockquote><p><em>dispatch</em></p><blockquote><p>state的修改 <strong>派发器</strong><br>通过派发器可以发送操作state的指令<br>具体修改行为由 <strong>reducer</strong> 执行</p></blockquote><p><strong>使用</strong></p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 购物车操作</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="title function_">cartReduce</span> = (<span class="params">state, action</span>) =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">const</span> newCart = &#123;...state&#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">switch</span> (action.<span class="property">type</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">case</span> <span class="string">&#x27;add&#x27;</span> :</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment">// 购物车添加</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment">// 判断购物车中是否已存在</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (newCart.<span class="property">items</span>.<span class="title function_">indexOf</span>(action.<span class="property">meal</span>) === -<span class="number">1</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="comment">// 不存在 往里面加</span></span><br><span class="line">                newCart.<span class="property">items</span>.<span class="title function_">push</span>(action.<span class="property">meal</span>)</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="comment">// 商品数量</span></span><br><span class="line">                action.<span class="property">meal</span>.<span class="property">amount</span> = <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">            &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                action.<span class="property">meal</span>.<span class="property">amount</span> += <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment">// 增加总数</span></span><br><span class="line">            newCart.<span class="property">totalAmount</span> += <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment">// 增加总价</span></span><br><span class="line">            newCart.<span class="property">totalPrice</span> += action.<span class="property">meal</span>.<span class="property">price</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> newCart;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">case</span> <span class="string">&#x27;remove&#x27;</span> :</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment">// 购物车删除</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment">// 减少商品数量</span></span><br><span class="line">            action.<span class="property">meal</span>.<span class="property">amount</span> -= <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment">// 检查商品数量是否为0</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (action.<span class="property">meal</span>.<span class="property">amount</span> === <span class="number">0</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                newCart.<span class="property">items</span>.<span class="title function_">splice</span>(newCart.<span class="property">items</span>.<span class="title function_">indexOf</span>(action.<span class="property">meal</span>), <span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment">// 修改商品金额和总数</span></span><br><span class="line">            newCart.<span class="property">totalAmount</span> -= <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">            newCart.<span class="property">totalPrice</span> -= action.<span class="property">meal</span>.<span class="property">price</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> newCart;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">default</span> :</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> state</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">const</span> [cartData, cartDispatch] = <span class="title function_">useReducer</span>(cartReduce, &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">items</span>: [],</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">totalAmount</span>: <span class="number">0</span>,</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">totalPrice</span>: <span class="number">0</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;)</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;<span class="title class_">CartContext</span>.<span class="property">Provider</span> value=&#123;&#123;...cartData, cartDispatch&#125;&#125;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">Cart</span>/&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    &lt;/<span class="title class_">CartContext</span>.<span class="property">Provider</span>&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 使用</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="title function_">addButtonHandler</span> = (<span class="params"></span>) =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        cartCtx.<span class="title function_">cartDispatch</span>(&#123;<span class="attr">type</span>: <span class="string">&#x27;add&#x27;</span>, <span class="attr">meal</span>: props.<span class="property">meal</span>&#125;)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="title function_">removeHandler</span> = (<span class="params"></span>) =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        cartCtx.<span class="title function_">cartDispatch</span>(&#123;<span class="attr">type</span>: <span class="string">&#x27;remove&#x27;</span>, <span class="attr">meal</span>: props.<span class="property">meal</span>&#125;)</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
